These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, action, animation
3 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, goat
1. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the owner of the mouse##7
2. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | action | family |
| Pet           | mouse  | goat     | pony  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, classical, folk
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, helicopter
1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person driving the car##7
3. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | punk | folk |
| Transport     | car       | helicopter     | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, hot-chocolate
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, bus
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person driving the bike##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | milk | cola | hot-chocolate  |
| Transport   | bus  | skateboard  | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, writer, musician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, epic, zombie
1. the dancer is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the writer##7
2. the person watching epic movies is not the dancer##6
3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | writer | dancer | musician     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | sports          | zombie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, r&b, blues
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, subway, ship
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the fan of r&b##7
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | blues     | r&b   |
| Transport     | ship | subway | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, ambient, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, russian
1. the dutch is on the left or right of the french##3
2. the french is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the russian##1
4. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the russian and the fan of indie##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | ambient     | indie     |
| Nationality   | russian | french | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | hedgehog       | ferret      | dog       |
| Sport   | biathlon | ice-hockey | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, videographer, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, superhero, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the videographer##7
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | software-developer | social-worker  | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster      | satire | superhero      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, fisherman, accountant
1. the accountant is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the nurse is somewhere between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | baking | collecting   |
| Job     | accountant    | nurse  | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, soccer
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is swimming##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | juice   | hot-chocolate    | cola |
| Sport      | soccer | water-polo | swimming |

