2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the french is not the person who's hobby is chess##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | chess | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | chinese    | australian    | french         |

