.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, papaya, cranberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, romance
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person eating apple##7
3. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | apple  | cranberry       | papaya     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | musical | mystery |

