.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, funk, dubstep
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the fan of soul and the fan of dubstep##7
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of soul and the person drinking juice##7
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | fanta     | almond-milk | juice |
| Music-Genre   | soul | funk    | dubstep |

