.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-14::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, plum, corn
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, taxi, tram
1. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
2. the person driving the tram is the person eating plum##1
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person eating cauliflower##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | plum | corn | cauliflower |
| Transport   | tram  | taxi       | van      |

