2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the person who's sport is badminton##7
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet     | pony  | snake       | lizard    |
| Sport   | soccer | skiing | badminton |

