2. the person eating zucchini is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating cucumber is somewhere between the german and the french##7
4. the french is the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | zucchini | cucumber     | artichoke   |
| Nationality   | german   | japanese | french |

