.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, social-worker, dressmaker
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the mechanic##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the social-worker##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | fanta      | hot-chocolate     | juice |
| Job        | dressmaker | mechanic | social-worker    |

 